summary: Add a starter cache of items in the torture room of Helgen Keep at the start of the game. If you missed it, you can go back through the dungeon and find the gear.
descriptionHtml: The mod adds a Prisoner's Belongings' chest in the torture room cage. Within the chest you can find a longbow, some iron arrows, some stormcloak armour, a novice hood, a novice robe of conjuration, a novice robe of destruction, and a novice robe of restoration. I also added the spell tomes Calm, Fear, Healing Hands, and Reanimate Corpse to the bench top, and various scrolls as well.
author: MysteryMan3
